<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
      xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8"/>
    <title>Owner History</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #222;
        }

        h1, h2, h3 {
            margin: 12px 0 8px;
        }

        .muted {
            color: #888;
        }

        .section {
            margin: 18px 0 28px;
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            border-spacing: 0;
            background: #fff;
        }

        th, td {
            border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
            padding: 8px 10px;
            vertical-align: top;
            text-align: center;
        }

        th {
            background: #f7f7f7;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .kv th {
            width: 30%;
        }

        .phase-head {
            display: flex;
            gap: 18px;
            align-items: baseline;
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 2px 6px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #555;
            background: #fafafa;
        }

        .grid {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .card {
            flex: 1 1 320px;
            min-width: 280px;
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #ececec;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, .03);
        }

        .card h3 {
            padding: 10px 12px;
            margin: 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
            font-size: 14px;
            background: #fcfcfc;
        }

        .card .content {
            padding: 10px 12px;
        }

        .nowrap {
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .subrow td {
            background: #fcfcfc;
            border-top: 0;
        }

        .table-plain th, .table-plain td {
            border: 0;
            border-bottom: 1px dashed #eee;
        }

        .table-plain tr:last-child td {
            border-bottom: 0;
        }

        /* handoff */
        .handoff-wrap {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .handoff-row {
            display: flex;
            align-items: stretch;
            gap: 12px;
            border: 1px solid #e8edf3;
            border-radius: 12px;
            background: #fff;
        }

        .handoff-left {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            padding: 10px 12px;
            min-width: 360px;
            border-right: 1px dashed #e8edf3;
        }

        .handoff-right {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 10px 12px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .h-node {
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border: 2px solid #ef4444;
            color: #b91c1c;
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: #fff;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .h-arrow {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #64748b;
            padding: 0 4px;
        }

        .h-line {
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            top: 50%;
            height: 2px;
            background: #f1f5f9;
        }

        .h-content {
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 8px 12px;
        }

        .h-chip {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 2px 8px;
            border-radius: 14px;
            background: #f7f9fc;
            border: 1px solid #e8edf3;
            color: #475467;
            font-size: 12px;
        }

        .h-summary {
            color: #334155;
        }

        .h-details {
            color: #667085;
            white-space: nowrap;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
        }

        @media (max-width: 1100px) {
            .handoff-left {
                min-width: 260px
            }

            .h-details {
                width: 100%
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body tal:define="
        phases   view/phases   | python: [];
        items    view/items    | python: [];
        analyses view/analyses | view/assigned_analyses | python: [];
        items_by_service python: dict(((i.get('service'), i) for i in (items or []) if isinstance(i, dict) and i.get('service')));
        to_u python: (lambda v: (isinstance(v, unicode) and v) or (isinstance(v, str) and v.decode('utf-8','ignore')) or unicode(v));
        ">

<div class="section">
    <h2>实验（样本）流转</h2>
    <div class="muted handoff-hint">提示：点击人员可筛选对应数据；再次点击可取消筛选（或按 ESC 清除）。</div>
    <div class="handoff-wrap"
             tal:define="
            _u python: to_u;
            phases_pre python: [p for p in (phases or []) if isinstance(p, dict) and p.get('key') in ('sample_due','sample_received')];
            ">
        <div tal:define="
                chain python:getattr(view, 'handoff_chain', {});
                nodes python:(chain and chain.get('nodes')) or [];
                node_ids python:(chain and chain.get('node_ids')) or [];
                ">

            <div tal:condition="python: bool(nodes)" class="handoff-row" style="margin:10px 0; padding:0;">
                <div class="handoff-left" style="width:100%; justify-content:flex-start;">
                    <div tal:repeat="i python:range(len(nodes))" style="display:inline;">
                        <span class="h-node js-chain-user"
                                 tal:content="python:nodes[i]"
                                 tal:attributes="
                                data-userid python:node_ids[i];
                                data-user   python:nodes[i];
                                ">User</span>
                        <span class="h-arrow" tal:condition="python:i != len(nodes)-1">→</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div tal:condition="python:not bool(nodes)" class="muted" style="margin:10px 0;">
                暂无流转记录
            </div>
        </div>

        <tal:block tal:condition="python:False">
            <div class="handoff-row" tal:repeat="ed view/user_handoffs">
                <div class="handoff-left">
                    <span class="h-node" tal:content="ed/frm">from</span>
                    <span class="h-arrow">→</span>
                    <span class="h-node" tal:content="ed/to">to</span>
                </div>

                <div class="handoff-right"
                         tal:define="
                        _u python: to_u;
                        when    python: _u(ed.get('when',''));
                        phase_t python: _u(ed.get('phase_title',''));
                        svc     python: _u(ed.get('service',''));
                        step_lb python: _u(ed.get('step_label',''));
                        state   python: _u(ed.get('state',''));
                        summary python:
                        (phase_t and u'(时间：%s，阶段：%s)' % (when or u'-', phase_t))
                        or u'(时间：%s，服务：%s，步骤：%s，状态：%s)' % (when, svc, step_lb, state);
                        details_text python: u'  ·  '.join([
                        u'%s / %s / %s / %s' % (
                        _u(d.get('when','')), _u(d.get('service','')),
                        _u(d.get('step_label','')), _u(d.get('state',''))
                        ) for d in (ed.get('details') or [])
                        ]);
                        ">
                    <span class="h-line"></span>
                    <div class="h-content">
                        <span class="h-summary h-chip" tal:content="summary"></span>
                        <span class="h-details" tal:condition="python: bool(details_text)" tal:content="details_text"></span>
                        <span class="h-details muted" tal:condition="python: not bool(details_text)">—</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="muted" tal:condition="python: not bool(view.user_handoffs)">
                暂无流转记录
            </div>
        </tal:block>

    </div>
</div>

<h1>样本处理历史</h1>

<!-- part 1-->
<div id="sec-phases" class="section" tal:condition="python: bool(phases)">
    <h2>阶段记录</h2>
    <div class="grid">
        <div class="card js-phase"
                 tal:repeat="p phases"
                 tal:attributes="
                data-userid python:(p.get('event',{}).get('actor') or '');
                data-user   python:(p.get('event',{}).get('actor_display') or '');
                ">
            <tal:block tal:define="is_dict python: isinstance(p, dict)">
                <h3>
                    <span tal:content="python:(is_dict and (p.get('title') or p.get('key') or u'阶段')) or to_u(p)">阶段</span>
                </h3>
                <div class="content">
                    <div class="phase-head" tal:condition="python: is_dict and bool(p.get('event'))">
                        <div class="badge"><span
                                class="nowrap">操作者：</span><strong tal:content="python:p.get('event',{}).get('actor_display',u'-')">-</strong>
                        </div>
                        <div class="badge"><span
                                class="nowrap">对象：</span><span tal:content="python:p.get('event',{}).get('obj_title_display',u'-')">-</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="badge"><span
                                class="nowrap">时间：</span><span tal:content="python:p.get('event',{}).get('time_str',u'-')">-</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <table class="kv" tal:condition="python:is_dict and bool(p.get('data'))">
                        <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>字段</th>
                            <th>值</th>
                        </tr>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody>
                        <tr tal:repeat="item python: sorted(p.get('data',{}).items(), key=lambda x: to_u(x[0]))">
                            <td tal:content="python: to_u(item[0])">字段</td>
                            <td tal:content="python:(to_u(item[1]) if item[1] not in (None,'') else u'-')">值</td>
                        </tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                    <div class="muted" tal:condition="python:is_dict and not bool(p.get('data'))">本阶段无结构化字段。
                    </div>
                </div>
            </tal:block>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- part2 -->
<div id="sec-analyses" class="section" tal:condition="python: bool(analyses)">
    <h2>实验分析项目</h2>
    <table id="analysis-table">
        <thead>
        <tr>
            <th>分析项目</th>
            <th>分析人员</th>
            <th class="nowrap">完成 / 总数</th>
        </tr>
        </thead>

        <tbody>
        <tal:rows tal:repeat="row analyses">
            <tal:block tal:define="
                    is_dict python: isinstance(row, dict);
                    svc     python: ((is_dict and row.get('service')) or ((not is_dict) and (len(row)>0 and row[0])) or u'-');
                    analyst python: ((is_dict and (row.get('analyst') or row.get('analyst_id'))) or ((not is_dict) and (len(row)>1 and row[1])) or u'-');
                    done    python: ((is_dict and row.get('done')) or ((not is_dict) and (len(row)>2 and row[2])));
                    total   python: ((is_dict and row.get('total')) or ((not is_dict) and (len(row)>3 and row[3])));
                    preferred_item python: (is_dict and (row.get('conditions') or row.get('results')) and row) or {};
                    item    python: preferred_item or items_by_service.get(svc,{});
                    ">

                <tr class="js-analysis-row"
                         tal:attributes="
                        data-userid python: (is_dict and (row.get('analyst_id') or '')) or '';
                        data-user   python: to_u(analyst);
                        ">

                    <td tal:content="python: to_u(svc)">项目</td>
                    <td tal:content="python: to_u(analyst)">人员</td>
                    <td tal:content="python: ((done is not None or total is not None) and (u'%s / %s' % (done or 0, total or 0))) or u'-'">
                        -
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="subrow js-analysis-row"
                         tal:condition="python: bool(item)"
                         tal:attributes="
                        data-userid python: (is_dict and (row.get('analyst_id') or '')) or '';
                        data-user   python: to_u(analyst);
                        ">
                    <td colspan="3">
                        <div style="display:flex;gap:16px;">
                            <div class="cond-col panel-box">
                                <strong>条件</strong>
                                <table class="table-plain" style="margin-top:6px;">
                                    <tbody tal:define="conds python: item.get('conditions') or {}">
                                    <tal:dict tal:condition="python:isinstance(conds,dict)">
                                        <tr tal:repeat="kv python: sorted(conds.items(), key=lambda x: to_u(x[0]))">
                                            <td tal:content="python: to_u(kv[0])">字段</td>
                                            <td tal:content="python:(to_u(kv[1]) if kv[1] not in (None,'',u'') else u'(未设置)')">
                                                值
                                            </td>
                                        </tr>
                                    </tal:dict>
                                    <tal:list tal:condition="python: not isinstance(conds,dict)">
                                        <tr tal:repeat="c conds" tal:define="
                                                is_map python:isinstance(c,dict);
                                                is_pair python:isinstance(c,(list,tuple)) and len(c)==2;
                                                title_raw python:(is_map and (c.get('title') or c.get('keyword'))) or (is_pair and c[0]) or c or u'-';
                                                value_raw python:(is_map and c.get('value')) or (is_pair and c[1]) or u'';
                                                title python: to_u(title_raw);
                                                value python:(isinstance(value_raw,(list,tuple)) and u', '.join([to_u(x) for x in value_raw])) or to_u(value_raw);
                                                ">
                                            <td tal:content="title">字段</td>
                                            <td tal:content="python:(value if value not in (None,u'', '') else u'(未设置)')">
                                                值
                                            </td>
                                        </tr>
                                    </tal:list>
                                    <tr tal:condition="python: not bool(conds)">
                                        <td colspan="2" class="muted">未设置任何条件</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    </tbody>
                                </table>
                            </div>

                            <div class="res-col panel-box">
                                <strong>结果</strong>
                                <table class="table-plain result-table" style="margin-top:6px;">
                                    <tbody tal:define="
                                            res python: item.get('results') or {};
                                            payloads python: item.get('results_payload') or {};
                                            ">
                                    <tr tal:repeat="kv python: sorted((res or {}).items(), key=lambda x: to_u(x[0]))">
                                        <td tal:content="python: to_u(kv[0])">字段</td>

                                        <td class="result-cell">
                                            <div tal:define="payload python: (payloads or {}).get(kv[0])">

                                                <!-- 普通文本 -->
                                                <div tal:condition="python: not bool(payload)"
                                                         tal:content="python:(to_u(kv[1]) if kv[1] not in (None,'',u'') else u'-')">
                                                    值
                                                </div>

                                                <div tal:condition="python: bool(payload)" class="result-panel">
                                                    <div tal:define="
                                                            vals python: (payload.get('values') or []);
                                                            imgs python: (payload.get('images') or []);
                                                            rows python: [(u'%1+',0),(u'%2+',1),(u'%3+',2),(u'%0',3),(u'H-score',4),(u'总和',5)];
                                                            ">
                                                        <div class="rp-row">

                                                            <div class="rp-metrics">
                                                                <table class="table-plain rp-metrics-table">
                                                                    <tbody>
                                                                    <tr tal:repeat="rr rows">
                                                                        <td class="rp-m-label" tal:content="python: rr[0]">
                                                                            label
                                                                        </td>
                                                                        <td class="rp-m-val" tal:content="python: (vals[rr[1]] if len(vals) > rr[1] else u'-')">
                                                                            0
                                                                        </td>
                                                                    </tr>
                                                                    </tbody>
                                                                </table>
                                                            </div>

                                                            <div class="rp-images" tal:condition="python: bool(imgs)">
                                                                <img tal:repeat="u imgs"
                                                                         tal:attributes="src python: to_u(u).strip()"
                                                                        class="rp-img"/>
                                                            </div>

                                                        </div>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>

                                            </div>
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                    </tbody>
                                </table>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </td>
                </tr>

                <tr class="subrow" tal:condition="python: not bool(item)">
                    <td colspan="3" class="muted">
                        该项目暂无可展示的条件/结果（未在行内或 items 中找到与
                        <span tal:replace="python: to_u(svc)">项目</span> 匹配的条目）。
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </tal:block>
        </tal:rows>
        </tbody>
    </table>
</div>

<!-- part 3 -->
<div id="sec-flow" class="section">
    <h2>流程流转</h2>
    <div id="analysis-empty-hint" class="muted" style="display:none; margin:8px 0;">
        当前人员在此样本中仅执行了<strong>分配/提交/复核</strong>等流程动作，没有生产表格等数据记录。
    </div>
</div>


<script type="text/javascript">
    (function () {
        function qsa(sel, root) {
            return Array.prototype.slice.call((root || document).querySelectorAll(sel));
        }

        function closest(el, sel) {
            while (el && el !== document) {
                if (el.matches && el.matches(sel)) return el;
                el = el.parentNode;
            }
            return null;
        }

        var activeId = null;
        var activeName = null;

        function applyFilter(userid, username) {
            activeId = userid || null;
            activeName = username || null;

            qsa(".js-chain-user").forEach(function (el) {
                var id = (el.getAttribute("data-userid") || "").trim();
                var nm = (el.getAttribute("data-user") || "").trim();
                var on = false;
                if (activeId && id) on = (id === activeId);
                else if (activeName) on = (nm === activeName);
                el.classList.toggle("is-active", on);
            });

            var phaseHit = 0;
            qsa(".js-phase").forEach(function (card) {
                var id = (card.getAttribute("data-userid") || "").trim();
                var nm = (card.getAttribute("data-user") || "").trim();

                if (!activeId && !activeName) {
                    card.style.display = "";
                    phaseHit += 1;
                    return;
                }

                var keep = false;
                if (activeId && id) keep = (id === activeId);
                else if (activeName) keep = (nm === activeName);

                card.style.display = keep ? "" : "none";
                if (keep) phaseHit += 1;
            });

            var analysisHit = 0;
            qsa(".js-analysis-row").forEach(function (row) {
                var id = (row.getAttribute("data-userid") || "").trim();
                var nm = (row.getAttribute("data-user") || "").trim();

                if (!activeId && !activeName) {
                    row.style.display = "";
                    analysisHit += 1;
                    return;
                }

                var keep = false;
                if (activeId && id) keep = (id === activeId);
                else if (activeName) keep = (nm === activeName);

                row.style.display = keep ? "" : "none";
                if (keep) analysisHit += 1;
            });

            var secPhases = document.getElementById("sec-phases");
            var secAnalyses = document.getElementById("sec-analyses");
            var secFlow = document.getElementById("sec-flow");
            var hint = document.getElementById("analysis-empty-hint");

            if (!activeId && !activeName) {
                if (secPhases) secPhases.style.display = "";
                if (secAnalyses) secAnalyses.style.display = "";
                if (secFlow) secFlow.style.display = "";
                if (hint) hint.style.display = "none";
                return;
            }

            if (secPhases) secPhases.style.display = (phaseHit > 0) ? "" : "none";
            if (secAnalyses) secAnalyses.style.display = (analysisHit > 0) ? "" : "none";
            var needFlow = (phaseHit === 0 && analysisHit === 0);
            if (secFlow) secFlow.style.display = needFlow ? "" : "none";
            if (hint) hint.style.display = needFlow ? "" : "none";
        }

        document.addEventListener("click", function (evt) {
            var node = closest(evt.target, ".js-chain-user");
            if (!node) return;

            var id = (node.getAttribute("data-userid") || "").trim();
            var nm = (node.getAttribute("data-user") || "").trim();

            var same = false;
            if (activeId && id && activeId === id) same = true;
            else if ((!activeId) && activeName && nm && activeName === nm) same = true;

            if (same) applyFilter(null, null);
            else applyFilter(id || null, nm || null);
        });

        // ESC清除
        document.addEventListener("keydown", function (e) {
            if (e.key === "Escape") applyFilter(null, null);
        });

        // 初始化默认选择最后一个操作者（已经完成操作）
        var chainNodes = qsa(".js-chain-user");
        if (chainNodes && chainNodes.length) {
            var last = chainNodes[chainNodes.length - 1];
            var id = (last.getAttribute("data-userid") || "").trim();
            var nm = (last.getAttribute("data-user") || "").trim();
            applyFilter(id || null, nm || null);
        } else {
            applyFilter(null, null);
        }

    })();
</script>
<style>
    .h-node.is-active {
        background: #ffecec;
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(255, 0, 0, .25) inset;
    }

    .result-panel {
        padding: 10px;
    }

    .result-panel .rp-row {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 16px;
    }

    .result-panel .rp-metrics {
        flex: 0 0 240px;
    }

    .result-panel .rp-metrics-table {
        width: 100%;
        border-collapse: collapse;
    }

    .result-panel .rp-metrics-table td {
        padding: 6px 8px;
        vertical-align: top;
    }

    .result-panel .rp-m-label {
        width: 60%;
        color: #444;
        white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .result-panel .rp-m-val {
        width: 40%;
        text-align: right;
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    .result-panel .rp-images {
        flex: 1 1 auto;
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 10px;
        align-content: flex-start;
    }

    .result-panel .rp-img {
        max-width: 260px;
        height: auto;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        background: #fff;
        padding: 2px;
    }

    td.result-cell {
        vertical-align: top;
        text-align: left;
        padding-top: 6px;
    }

    .cond-col {
        flex: 0 0 260px;
        min-width: 220px;
        max-width: 320px;
    }

    .cond-col .table-plain td {
        padding: 4px 8px;
        white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .cond-col .table-plain td:last-child {
        white-space: normal;
        word-break: break-all;
    }

    .res-col {
        flex: 1 1 auto;
        min-width: 520px;
    }

    .res-col .table-plain td {
        padding: 4px 8px;
        vertical-align: top;
    }

    .res-col .table-plain td:first-child {
        width: 180px; /* 结果字段名固定窄一点 */
        white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .res-col .table-plain td:last-child {
        word-break: break-all;
        white-space: normal;
    }

    .panel-box {
        border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
        border-radius: 6px;
        padding: 10px 12px;
        background: #fff;
    }

    .panel-box strong {
        display: block;
        margin: 0 0 8px 0;
        font-size: 14px;
    }

    .result-table {
        width: 100%;
    }

    .result-table td {
        padding: 5px 10px;
        vertical-align: top;
    }

    .result-table tr td:first-child {
        width: 220px;
        color: #333;
        font-weight: 500;
        white-space: nowrap;
        overflow: hidden;
        text-overflow: ellipsis;
    }

    .result-table tr td:last-child {
        color: #111;
        text-align: left;
        white-space: normal;
        word-break: break-all;
    }

    .result-table tr td:last-child.is-num {
        text-align: right;
        font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    }

    .handoff-hint {
        margin: 6px 0 10px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #2c3e50;
        font-weight: 600;
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 6px;
        padding: 6px 10px;
        border: 1px solid #e6eefc;
        border-radius: 6px;
        background: #f7fbff;
    }

    .handoff-hint:before {
        content: "\1F449";
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1100px) {
        .cond-col {
            flex: 1 1 100%;
            max-width: none;
        }

        .res-col {
            flex: 1 1 100%;
            min-width: 0;
        }
    }
</style>
</body>
</html>
